<section id="about-us">
  <div class="about container">
    <h1 class="about-heading">About</h1>
    <p class="description">The idea for Fineapple Studios started with 3 college classmates, including myself, who had grown up with a love for music, particularly music with Asian-American cultural influence.
      The vision of the label is to form a collective of young, upcoming artists that seek to build on their creative capacity and curate relevant experiences that contribute to the culture.
      Note that this website only serves as a <i>template</i> for further expansion for the label's content and ideas. It should be viewed only as such and treated by no means as a final product.</p>
    <p class="disclaimer"><i>Important note on links:</i> There are currently no actual social media accounts owned by Fineapple Studios. The links displayed at the website's footer are present for cosmetic purposes only and will only redirect
      to each platform's corresponding home page. On the other hand, please keep in mind that the social media links displayed on each member's profile will take you to each of their real accounts. </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="who-we-are">
  <div class="container-fluid members">
    <h1 class="members-heading">Our Members</h1>
    <h2 class="members-subheading">Meet the founders</h2>

    <div class="row member-row"> <!-- Address how this can be scaled -->
      <% founders.forEach(function(founder){ %>
        <div class="member-profile col-lg-4">
          <a href="/founder-profile/<%= founder.firstName %>"><img class="member-image" src="Photos/<%= founder.imageIcon %>" alt="..."></a>
          <h4><a class="bio-link" href="/founder-profile/<%= founder.firstName %>"><%= founder.firstName %> <%= founder.lastName %></a></h4>
          <i><%= founder.roleDescription %></i>
        </div>
      <% }); %>
    </div>
    <h2 class="members-subheading">Meet the artists</h2>
    <div class="row member-row"> <!-- Address how this can be scaled -->
      <% artists.forEach(function(artist){ %>
      <div class="member-profile col-lg-6">
        <a href="/artist-profile/<%= artist.firstName %>"><img class="member-image" src="Photos/<%= artist.imageIcon %>" alt="..."></a>
        <h4><a class="bio-link" href="/artist-profile/<%= artist.firstName %>"><%= artist.firstName %> <%= artist.lastName %></a></h4>
        <i><%= artist.roleDescription %></i>
      </div>
      <% }); %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
